Problem: Best Time to Buy and Sell Stock
Topic: Arrays
Difficulty: Easy
Approach:
Use two pointers where one tracks the minimum price so far (buy day) and the other scans future prices (sell day). Update the maximum profit whenever a higher profit is found, and update the buy pointer when a lower price is encountered.
Time Complexity: O(n)
Space Complexity: O(1)

